    "_srcBlendFactor": 770,
    "_dstBlendFactor": 771,
    "_string": "All symbols EXCEPT SCATTER and JACKPOT symbol pay left to right on each \nwinning combination, when appearing on adjacent reels, \nstarting with the leftmost reel.\n\nAll wins will be multiplied by 1/100 of total bet.\nOnly the highest win combination per way is paid.\n\nEvery spin is played with a maximum number of paylines.\n\nPaytable presents wins for a bet equal to 1 coin and one winning payline.\nBet 10 will give you 10x the payout from the pay table.",
    "_N$string": "All symbols EXCEPT SCATTER and JACKPOT symbol pay left to right on each \nwinning combination, when appearing on adjacent reels, \nstarting with the leftmost reel.\n\nAll wins will be multiplied by 1/100 of total bet.\nOnly the highest win combination per way is paid.\n\nEvery spin is played with a maximum number of paylines.\n\nPaytable presents wins for a bet equal to 1 coin and one winning payline.\nBet 10 will give you 10x the payout from the pay table.",
